FitNesse Maven plugin

* Limitation

  The plugin can't executed the {{{run-mojo.html}fitnesse:run}} with FitNesse 20060719. See  {{{http://jira.codehaus.org/browse/MOJO-778}MOJO-778}} for more information.

* Goals Overview

  General Information about the goals.

  * {{{run-mojo.html}fitnesse:run}} execute locally FitNesse 'Suites' and/or ''Tests''.
  
  * {{{remotecall-mojo.html}fitnesse:remotecall}} get result of remote FitNesse execution.
  
  * {{{fitnesse-mojo.html}fitnesse:fitnesse}} create FitNesse report.

* Usage

  Instructions on how to use the FitNesse plugin can be found {{{usage.html}here}}.

* FAQ

  The FAQ can be found {{{faq.html}here}}.
  
  If you don't use Maven2 for you build, but you're interested by executing remote FitNesse page locally? See {{{faq.html#DoINeedAWholeMaven2Build}there}}.

